---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Open Beta Disclaimer — Rift Wars" description="Open Beta disclaimer for Rift Wars by Meta Machina Studio LLC. Information about beta testing, server stability, and data expectations.">
  <section class="section-padding pt-32 bg-mm-bg">
    <div class="section-container max-w-3xl">
      <div class="inline-block px-4 py-1 mb-6 bg-[#fbbf24] border-[1.5px] border-[#fbbf24] rounded-sm" style="box-shadow: 0 0 12px rgba(251,191,36,0.5), 0 0 25px rgba(251,191,36,0.2);">
        <span class="font-orbitron text-xs font-bold tracking-[3px] text-black uppercase">Open Beta</span>
      </div>
      <h1 class="font-orbitron text-3xl font-bold text-mm-text mb-8 neon-text">Beta Disclaimer</h1>

      <div class="prose prose-invert max-w-none space-y-6">
        <p class="font-exo text-mm-text2">Last updated: April 8, 2026</p>
        <p class="font-exo text-mm-text2 leading-relaxed">
          Rift Wars is currently in <strong>Open Beta</strong>. By accessing or playing the game during this period,
          you acknowledge and agree to the following terms. This disclaimer supplements and is incorporated into our
          <a href="/terms" class="text-mm-cyan hover:underline">Terms of Service</a>.
        </p>

        <h2 class="font-orbitron text-lg text-mm-cyan mt-8 mb-3">1. Beta Status</h2>
        <p class="font-exo text-mm-text2 leading-relaxed">
          Rift Wars is an actively developing product that has not yet reached its final release state.
          The game, its features, content, and services are provided on an <strong>"as is" and "as available"</strong> basis.
          During the Open Beta period, all aspects of the game — including but not limited to gameplay mechanics,
          card statistics, economy values, user interface, and available features — are subject to change,
          modification, or removal at any time without prior notice.
        </p>

        <h2 class="font-orbitron text-lg text-mm-cyan mt-8 mb-3">2. Server Stability & Downtime</h2>
        <p class="font-exo text-mm-text2 leading-relaxed">
          During the Open Beta testing period, you may experience:
        </p>
        <ul class="font-exo text-mm-text2 leading-relaxed list-disc ml-6 space-y-1">
          <li>Unscheduled server downtime, outages, or interruptions</li>
          <li>Scheduled maintenance windows for updates, patches, and infrastructure changes</li>
          <li>Performance degradation, latency spikes, or connectivity issues</li>
          <li>Server restarts that may interrupt active matches</li>
          <li>Service unavailability during infrastructure migrations or upgrades</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="font-exo text-mm-text2 leading-relaxed">
          <strong>Meta Machina Studio LLC makes no guarantees of uptime, availability, or service continuity
          during the Open Beta period.</strong> We will make reasonable efforts to minimize disruptions but cannot
          be held liable for any downtime or its effects on your gameplay experience.
        </p>

        <h2 class="font-orbitron text-lg text-mm-cyan mt-8 mb-3">3. Data & Progress</h2>
        <p class="font-exo text-mm-text2 leading-relaxed">
          While we intend to preserve player data and progress through and beyond the beta period,
          we reserve the right to:
        </p>
        <ul class="font-exo text-mm-text2 leading-relaxed list-disc ml-6 space-y-1">
          <li>Reset, modify, or wipe player accounts, inventories, rankings, or currency balances</li>
          <li>Alter the value, function, or availability of in-game items and currencies (including M-Credz)</li>
          <li>Rebalance card statistics, abilities, economy rates, or matchmaking parameters</li>
          <li>Remove or restructure features that were previously available</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="font-exo text-mm-text2 leading-relaxed">
          In the event of a data reset, we will provide advance notice when reasonably possible.
          No compensation is guaranteed for progress or items lost due to beta-related resets or changes.
        </p>

        <h2 class="font-orbitron text-lg text-mm-cyan mt-8 mb-3">4. Bug Reporting & Feedback</h2>
        <p class="font-exo text-mm-text2 leading-relaxed">
          Beta testers are encouraged to report bugs, exploits, and feedback through our official channels,
          including our <a href="https://discord.gg/metamachina" class="text-mm-cyan hover:underline" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Discord server</a>.
          Exploiting known bugs or glitches for competitive advantage during the beta period is a violation of our
          <a href="/terms" class="text-mm-cyan hover:underline">Terms of Service</a> and may result in account suspension.
        </p>

        <h2 class="font-orbitron text-lg text-mm-cyan mt-8 mb-3">5. No Warranty</h2>
        <p class="font-exo text-mm-text2 leading-relaxed">
          THE OPEN BETA SERVICE IS PROVIDED WITHOUT WARRANTY OF ANY KIND, EXPRESS OR IMPLIED, INCLUDING BUT NOT LIMITED TO
          WARRANTIES OF MERCHANTABILITY, FITNESS FOR A PARTICULAR PURPOSE, AND NON-INFRINGEMENT. META MACHINA STUDIO LLC
          DOES NOT WARRANT THAT THE SERVICE WILL BE UNINTERRUPTED, ERROR-FREE, SECURE, OR FREE OF VIRUSES OR OTHER
          HARMFUL COMPONENTS DURING THE BETA PERIOD.
        </p>

        <h2 class="font-orbitron text-lg text-mm-cyan mt-8 mb-3">6. Limitation of Liability</h2>
        <p class="font-exo text-mm-text2 leading-relaxed">
          TO THE MAXIMUM EXTENT PERMITTED BY APPLICABLE LAW, META MACHINA STUDIO LLC SHALL NOT BE LIABLE FOR ANY
          INDIRECT, INCIDENTAL, SPECIAL, CONSEQUENTIAL, OR PUNITIVE DAMAGES ARISING OUT OF OR RELATED TO YOUR
          USE OF THE BETA SERVICE, INCLUDING BUT NOT LIMITED TO LOSS OF DATA, LOSS OF PROGRESS, LOSS OF VIRTUAL
          ITEMS OR CURRENCY, OR INTERRUPTION OF GAMEPLAY, REGARDLESS OF WHETHER SUCH DAMAGES WERE FORESEEABLE
          OR WHETHER META MACHINA STUDIO LLC WAS ADVISED OF THE POSSIBILITY OF SUCH DAMAGES.
        </p>

        <h2 class="font-orbitron text-lg text-mm-cyan mt-8 mb-3">7. Changes to This Disclaimer</h2>
        <p class="font-exo text-mm-text2 leading-relaxed">
          We reserve the right to update this Beta Disclaimer at any time. Changes take effect immediately upon posting.
          Continued use of the Service after any changes constitutes acceptance of the updated terms.
          When the game exits Open Beta and reaches full release, this disclaimer will be retired and the standard
          <a href="/terms" class="text-mm-cyan hover:underline">Terms of Service</a> will govern all use.
        </p>

        <h2 class="font-orbitron text-lg text-mm-cyan mt-8 mb-3">8. Contact</h2>
        <p class="font-exo text-mm-text2 leading-relaxed">
          For questions about this Beta Disclaimer or to report issues, contact us at:
        </p>
        <ul class="font-exo text-mm-text2 leading-relaxed list-disc ml-6 space-y-1">
          <li>Discord: <a href="https://discord.gg/metamachina" class="text-mm-cyan hover:underline" target="_blank" rel="noopener">discord.gg/metamachina</a></li>
          <li>X: <a href="https://x.com/MetaMachina_RW" class="text-mm-cyan hover:underline" target="_blank" rel="noopener">@MetaMachina_RW</a></li>
        </ul>

        <div class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-white/10">
          <p class="font-exo text-mm-text2/60 text-sm">
            &copy; 2026 Meta Machina Studio LLC. All rights reserved. Nevada, United States.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
